<inglise> Whereas several issues relating to consumer health are of a multidisciplinary nature and require input from various scientific committees which would benefit from an effective coordination; </inglise>
<eesti> mitmed tarbija tervishoiuga seotud k&uuml;simused on mitme teadusharu vahelised ja n&otilde;uavad eri teaduskomiteede panust ning k&otilde;nealuseid teaduskomiteesid oleks kasulik t&otilde;husalt koordineerida; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Commission must be able to obtain sound and timely scientific advice; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjon peab saama &otilde;igeaegselt usaldusv&auml;&auml;rseid teadusalaseid n&otilde;uandeid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas scientific advice on matters relating to consumer health must, in the interests of consumers and industry, be based on the principles of excellence, independence and transparency, </inglise>
<eesti> tarbija tervishoidu puudutavate k&uuml;simustega seotud teadusalased n&otilde;uanded peavad tarbijate ja t&ouml;&ouml;stuse huvides p&otilde;hinema kompetentsusel, s&otilde;ltumatusel ja l&auml;bipaistvusel, </eesti>
